45, \"to\": 759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Obviously there are special circumstances and people who need help, but as a general 'look how cool, she did not even have to write anything herself!'\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 911, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"special circumstances\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 802}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 813}, {\"ngram\": \"help\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 827}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 901}]}, {\"sentence\": \"story, it SUCKS.\", \"from\": 912, \"to\": 928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Who wants an AI-written fan letter??\\\"\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 966, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an AI-written fan letter\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Holmes went on to say that fan letters are \\\"a great way for a kid to learn to write,\\\" and encouraging children to use AI for writing would prevent them from learning how to improve their writing skills.\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 1170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 968, \"end\": 974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sherlock_Holmes\", \"score\": 0.9999055836299974, \"rank\": 9.442528526191391e-05, \"text\": \"Holmes\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sherlock_Holmes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sherlock_Holmes\"}, {\"begin\": 1086, \"end\": 1088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.299955181312914e-19, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fan letters\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1006}, {\"ngram\": \"a great way\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1023}, {\"ngram\": \"a kid\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1033}, {\"ngram\": \"children\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1078}, {\"ngram\": \"writing\", 